# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in version control.
#   However, in case of collaboration, if lock is used, it may affect other environments.
#   So, it's a choice.
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock can be submitted or ignored depending on your preference:
#   https://python-poetry.org/docs/basic-usage/#commit-your-poetrylock-file-to-version-control
#poetry.lock

# pdm
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, pdm.lock can be submitted or ignored depending on your preference:
#   https://pdm.fming.dev/#recommendations
#pdm.lock

